
Installing on linux (Ubuntu 20.04, debian bullseye)
===================================================

== already installed
== install (with apt-get,  aptitude)
mpv
libmpv-dev
git
python3
    -matplotlib  (voorlopig 3.1.3)
    -numpy
    -scipy
    -pyqt5       (voorlopig 5.12.3)
    -pyqt5.qtquick
    -pip
    -yaml
    -openpyxl
    -mplcursors
qtdeclarative5-dev
qt5-default
qml-module-qtquick-layout
                  -dialogs
		  -controls
		  -controls2
qml-module-qt-labs-settings
qml-module-qt-labs-folderlistmodel
texlive
texlive-latex-extra

== install with pip3
  pylatex
  python-mpv

  maybe pyqt5 and matplotlib need to be downgraded to the mentioned versions above.
  
== the versions should be fairly recent, otherwise there are warnings or errors.
- Basic testing
    - Command:  pdflatex tstlatex.tex
       - yields a pdf file
    - Command:  python tstqtquick.py
       - yields a yellow window
    - Command:  python tstmatplotlib.py
       - a simple plot



